OL,3,CNI energy suppliers slash prices
OL,5,FEnergy suppliers in Northern Ireland
OL,6,Fhave announced price decreases
OL,7,Ffollowing a fall in wholesale market
OL,8,Fcosts.JIt comes after a Utility
OL,9,FRegulator review of the regulated
OL,10,Ftariffs for Power NI and SSE
OL,11,FAirtricity Gas Supply.JFrom April 1,
OL,12,FPower NI's domestic tariff will reduce
OL,13,Fby 6.3%, or #64 per year, whilst SSE
OL,14,FAirtricity Gas Supply's tariff for
OL,15,Fdomestic and small business customers
OL,16,Fin the Greater Belfast and West gas
OL,17,Fareas will reduce by 22.8%, or #320
OL,18,Fper year.
