OL,3,CNI energy suppliers slash prices
OL,5,FAn announcement around Firmus Energy's
OL,6,Fregulated gas tariff is set to be made
OL,7,Fnext week.
OL,9,FBudget Energy also announced a price
OL,10,Fcut of 9% for their customers from
OL,11,Ftoday. The company which has about
OL,12,F80,000 customers across Northern
OL,13,FIreland announced the price cut last
OL,14,Fmonth.
OL,16,FIt said the price cut was due to
OL,17,Ffurther reductions in energy wholesale
OL,18,Fcosts. The reduction will result in a
OL,19,Fsaving of around #110 per year for a
OL,20,Ftypical prepay customer.
